# UI Interactions

- Motion from CSS tokens (`--motion-fast`, `--motion-medium`, `--motion-spring`) in `base.css`.
- Interactive surfaces use rounded theme shapes; `Card.tsx` for tappable cards.
- Confirm bars slide up with spring curve; sheets use `BottomSheet.tsx`.
- **PWA shell** (tab bar, `PageTransition`, edge stagger) lives here — not in `components/ui/**/mobile/`. Load `shell-viewport-motion.md`.

Load `.cursor/skills/project/ui-interactions/SKILL.md` when adding buttons, cards, navigation, or animations.
